\[|a - z| + |z - w| + |w - b| \ge |a - b|,\]so
\[|z - w| \ge |a - b| - |a - z| - |w - b|.\]We have that $|a - b| = |(-1 - 3i) - (7 + 8i) = |-8 - 11i| = \sqrt{185}.$  Also, $|a - z| = 1$ and $|w - b| = 3,$ so
